OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mild night
OL,6,Ffor many with high cloud clearing to
OL,7,Fgive clear spells later on. Cooler in
OL,8,Frural areas with a slight chance of
OL,9,Ffog patches developing in places with
OL,10,Fthe winds remaining light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA warm or very warm day with
OL,13,Flight winds and plenty of sunshine for
OL,14,Fmost. Feeling a little cooler along
OL,15,Fthe coast with the sea breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
