OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FSunny
OL,6,Fand very warm or hot for most on
OL,7,FMonday. Temperature may start to
OL,8,Fslowly decrease on Tuesday and
OL,9,FWednesday but still remaining above
OL,10,Faverage for the time of year.
